hu.trigary.iodine.api.gui.element

Interface RadioButtonGuiElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AttachmentHolder<RadioButtonGuiElement>, DrawPrioritizeable<RadioButtonGuiElement>, GuiEditable<RadioButtonGuiElement>, GuiElement<RadioButtonGuiElement>, GuiTooltipable<RadioButtonGuiElement>

    public interface RadioButtonGuiElement
extends GuiElement<RadioButtonGuiElement>, GuiEditable<RadioButtonGuiElement>, GuiTooltipable<RadioButtonGuiElement>
    A GUI element that is a radio button. Radio buttons are linked together by their common group-ID, which is '0' by default.
